verbose_text: Tigchelaar et al.40 disclose an investigation into the intramolecular [4 +2] cycloadditions of diene tethered alkynyl halides 43 catalyzed by iridium, specifically with the use of [IrCl (cod)] 2 or IrCl (CO) (PPh 3) 2 as the catalyst and PPh 3 or BINAP as the ligand (Scheme XREF_FIG, Table XREF_TABLE).
evidence: catalyzed by iridium, specifically with the use of [IrCl(cod)] 2  or IrCl(CO)(PPh 3 ) 2
